e:T6ea,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Jasper better than Surfer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Jasper scores 8.0 overall while Surfer scores 8.0. Jasper is best for marketing teams and ad copy, while Surfer excels for SEO optimization and content scoring."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Jasper or Surfer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Jasper starts at $49/mo and Surfer starts at $89/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Jasper to Surfer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Jasper and Surfer support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Jasper vs Surfer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Jasper holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Surfer has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Jasper for 50+ templates for marketing use cases and Surfer for best-in-class content scoring against serp competitors."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Jasper or Surfer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Jasper for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Surfer remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize best-in-class content scoring against serp competitors. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h1",null,{"